A library for working with .blu sound description files for _why's Bloopsaphone. Use thusly:

    Blu.load(my_bloop, "path/to/sound.blu")
    
Coming soon: sound serialization. More about Bloopsaphone here: http://github.com/mental/bloopsaphone

Contribute your sounds to the Bloopsbank! http://github.com/atduskgreg/bloopsbank/tree